<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Nov1928"><font color="red">16 November 1928</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Valery Larbaud): (written in heavy black pencil) These few lines to tell you my wife was operated on the 8 &hellip; we go home in a day or so and then, after 15 days autovaccine treatment return here for 4 days more radium &hellip; I can see my own handwriting in this black graphite but cannot see one word of any print but capitals! </div>
